1
00:00:06,292 --> 00:00:08,894
Hello, my name is Yoshifumi Hashimoto,

2
00:00:08,894 --> 00:00:11,516
the executive officer and CCO of Marvelous AQL.

3
00:00:11,516 --> 00:00:12,597
Today, I'm going to talk about how to make an RPG.

4
00:00:12,597 --> 00:00:14,318
My main focus is the role of a producer.

5
00:00:14,318 --> 00:00:15,119
In terms of the work involved,

6
