I take helm of various projects.

7
00:00:15,879 --> 00:00:16,640
But depending on the game,

8
00:00:35,515 --> 00:00:40,579
I'll take on the role of an all-around supporter or write the scenario and even come up with

9
00:00:40,579 --> 00:00:43,041
settings and names, and at times attend voiceover recordings and act as an audio director.

10
00:00:43,041 --> 00:00:47,545
When I get heavily involved, I'll get into the game design and decide what kind of game

11
00:00:47,545 --> 00:00:48,926
we're going to make.

12
00:01:06,337 --> 00:01:10,818
I simply love making things, so I try to get involved on various aspects of the projects

13
00:01:10,818 --> 00:01:11,198
that we're doing.

14
